name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ex rel. Francis KIRSHNER, Petitioner v. Honorable Shelly Robins NEW, Warden John Delaney, CFCF, Respondents
name_abbreviation: Commonwealth ex rel. Kirshner v. New

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ex rel. Francis KIRSHNER, Petitioner v. Honorable Shelly Robins NEW, Warden John Delaney, CFCF, Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 9th day of March, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the jurist’s name from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
